The Load Template command allows you to load a previously created template (.
</S>
<S ID="47146">
@tm) file.
</S>
<S ID="47238">
A template file contains a set of zones (and links) that you defined in the preview window.
</S>
<S ID="47367">
When you click Load Template in the main window, a subwindow opens, letting you locate and load the template file (Figure 3-10).
