<S ID="135284">
The following subsections describe how to perform verification tasks, specifically how to:
</S>
<S ID="135310">
Accept a character group
</S>
<S ID="135331">
Accept a whole word
</S>
<S ID="135368">
Make corrections and accept changes
</S>
<S ID="135407">
Make corrections without verification
</S>
