</S>
<S ID="226139">
, the ScanWorX text conversion process,, wherein recognized text is converted to the specified output format
</S>
<S ID="226151">
Previewing
</S>
<S ID="226187">
, the ScanWorX previewing capability
</S>
<S ID="226199">
Processing
</S>
<S ID="226238">
, the ScanWorX text recognition process
</S>
